WEBVTT

00:01.029 --> 00:02.196
Attention, boys and ghouls.

00:02.231 --> 00:03.831
Nope.

00:03.866 --> 00:05.600
Every Halloween, I dress up
in an amazing costume,

00:05.601 --> 00:07.402
and you never get what I am.
<i>No, we get what you are...</i>

00:07.436 --> 00:09.837
An adult man
who enjoys dress-up.

00:09.872 --> 00:11.139
Very funny, Rosa.

00:11.140 --> 00:13.474
This year,
that won't be a problem

00:13.475 --> 00:15.877
because you're gonna
pick my costume.

00:19.448 --> 00:20.882
Uh, Ms. Pac-man's nipple.

00:20.916 --> 00:22.517
No, that's brown.

00:22.551 --> 00:23.584
Why would you know that?

00:23.619 --> 00:26.721
To be or not to be!
Not to be.

00:26.722 --> 00:28.056
Thank you.

00:29.725 --> 00:31.359
Joan of Arc.
Rod Stewart.

00:31.360 --> 00:32.360
Martha Stewart.

00:32.360 --> 00:34.695
He-man!
Master of the universe.

00:34.730 --> 00:36.697
I got it.
Gay Robin Hood.

00:36.698 --> 00:37.865
Yes!

00:37.900 --> 00:39.133
<i>That's it, that's it.</i>

00:39.134 --> 00:41.402
<i>That's what it is.</i>

